    <record id="savvy_stewards" model="res.partner.segment">
        <field name="name">Savvy Stewards</field>
        <field name="main_driver">I need to direct my giving where I trust it will achieve maximum impact.</field>
        <field name="segment_index">1</field>
        <field name="survey_result" type="html">
            <p>It’s so great that you are interested in getting more facts, information and numbers from us! For about 70 years we at Compassion attach a great deal of importance to the efficiency of invested funds in the fight against extreme poverty and for the childrens’ development.</p>
            <p>Thank you for your trust. We commit to informing you about the impact of your support for children in the Global South.</p>
            <p>Did you know? We guarantee that at least 80% of sponsorship donations - for gifts to your sponsored child and fund donations up to 100% -  are invested in projects and programmes in the countries of the South. Thank you for the considerable impact you’ve already made.</p>
            <p>Thank you for your precious support.</p>
        </field>
