        <field name="survey_result" type="html">
            <p>It’s so great that your faith inspires your generous giving. It’s also delightful that you seek to know your sponsored child and Compassion on a deeper, more personal level. Thank you from the bottom of our hearts.
Thanks to our holistic approach to child development, we commit to a personal and all-round support to the child on a physical, cognitive, socio-emotional and spiritual level through one of the 8000 Compassion partner churches.
</p>
